subject: Re: Junit.jar source code
msgSnippet: If you download the 3.8.1 distribution (junit3.8.1.zip, available from junit.org), they are in src.jar Or you can download them from cvs: cvs
messageBody:
If you download the 3.8.1 distribution (junit3.8.1.zip, available from
junit.org), they are in src.jar

Or you can download them from cvs:

cvs -d:pserver:anonymous@...:/cvsroot/junit login

(no password)

cvs -z3 -d:pserver:anonymous@...:/cvsroot/junit co -P
modulename



Instructions can be found on:
http://sourceforge.net/cvs/?group_id=15278

Regards, Jan
